": {"name": "str | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "Post", "xref": {"fqname": "x_lolo.session.post.Post", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Adds a new post (tweet) to the session.\n\n```\nparam text\n\nThe text content of the post\n\nparam media_url\n\nURL of the media to attach (optional)\n\nreturn\n\nThe created Post object\n```\n"]}, {"name": "x_lolo.session.Session.get_user_by_username", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "username", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "User", "xref": {"fqname": "x_lolo.session.user.User", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Fetches user data by username.\n\nThis method retrieves user information based on their Twitter/X username.\nThe response is then parsed to create and return a User object.\n\n```\nparam username\n\nThe Twitter/X username to fetch data for\n\nreturn\n\nA User object containing the fetched user data\n\nraises Exception\n\nIf the API request fails or returns an unexpected status code\n```\n"]}, {"name": "x_lolo.session.Session.me", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "User", "xref": {"fqname": "x_lolo.session.user.User", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Fetches the current authenticated user's data .\n\nThis method retrieves information about the user who is currently authenticated in the session.\nThe response is then parsed to create and return a User object representing the current user.\n\n```\nreturn\n\nA User object containing the fetched data for the current authenticated user\n\nraises Exception\n\nIf the API request fails or returns an unexpected status code\n```\n"]}, {"name": "x_lolo.session.Session.get_user_posts", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "user_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqna